---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="연락처 | 깃냥이.DEV" description="깃냥이에게 연락하기">
  <article class="contact-page">
    <h1>연락처</h1>

    <section class="contact-intro">
      <p>궁금한 점이나 함께 이야기 나누고 싶은 주제가 있다면 언제든 연락 주세요.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-methods">
      <div class="contact-item">
        <h2>GitHub</h2>
        <p>
          <a href="https://github.com/yepp04" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            github.com/yepp04
          </a>
        </p>
        <p class="description">이슈나 PR을 통해 연락하실 수 있습니다.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-item">
        <h2>이메일</h2>
        <p class="description">
          GitHub 프로필을 통해 연락해주세요.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-item">
        <h2>포트폴리오</h2>
        <p>
          <a href="https://jinseong.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            jinseong.dev
          </a>
        </p>
        <p class="description">더 자세한 정보와 프로젝트를 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .contact-page {
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .contact-intro p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .contact-methods {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-item {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .contact-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .description {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
</style>
